[normal] Sightsavers (2013) 
[normal]Supporti
[normal]ng inclusive Development: Uganda’s experience of implementing the UNCRPD
[normal] DFID has experience of providing training in this area: Through the Knowledge and Research programme DFID ran Disability Equality Training. This provided appropriate disability-incl
[normal]usive training to key staff members. 
